summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the new assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1637, under Ordinance No. 18904, for the improvement of the alley in block 8, D. S. Maynard's Plat of the Town (now City) of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 17429, and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land, and part thereof, shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
